nodes.text: The Coruscant Holo Net: Who was "Zatch"?

The Coruscant Holo Net: Who was "Zatch"? was an in-universe issue of The Coruscant Holo Net that was published in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.50. It was later reprinted in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 21. It extrapolated on events featured in the comic story The Runaway Ride.
